title: Basketball HOF and All-Time Starting Five's with Twitter's Chris Barnett
itunes:title: Basketball HOF and All-Time Starting Five's with Twitter's Chris Barnett
description:
Miles and Jack were pleased to be joined by the Founder of Twitter's Hoop Spaces, Chris Barnett on the latest episode of Mad Boosties. The trio discussed the 2022 Basketball Hall of Fame class, AI's all-time starting 5 and Philly's chances in the Eastern Conference this upcoming season.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
